    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You bless up to three creatures of your choice within range. Whenever a target makes an attack roll or a saving throw before the spell ends, the target can roll a [[/r d4]] and add the number rolled to the attack roll or saving throw.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p></p><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"At Higher Levels\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, you can target one additional creature for each slot level above 1st.</p></div></div>",
